    "result": {"data":{"cur":{"id":"4cab7591-3237-57bf-9efe-96504ea26003","html":"<h2 id=\"webgl-이란\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#webgl-%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\" aria-label=\"webgl 이란 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>WebGL 이란?</h2>\n<p>WebGL은 OpenGL을 기반으로 하는 JavaScript API / Library로 웹 브라우저가 추가 플러그인, 타사 플로그인 또는 브라우저 확장 프로그램을 설치할 필요 없이 브라우저에서 3D / 2D 그래픽을 렌더링을 도와준다. WebGL을 사용하면 브라우저를 통해 GPU를 사용하여 3D 그래픽을 HTML 페이지로 렌더링 할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"threejs\"\n        title=\"threejs\"\n        src=\"/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/37523/threejs.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/e9ff0/threejs.png 180w,\n/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/f21e7/threejs.png 360w,\n/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/37523/threejs.png 720w,\n/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/302a4/threejs.png 1080w,\n/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/07a9c/threejs.png 1440w,\n/static/6a97ee2d74340a88e68138f2879c4859/9ac09/threejs.png 2204w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<p><a href=\"https://threejs.org/\">Three.js</a></p>\n</div>\n<br>\n<p>아래 사이트는 다양한 개발 샘플이 있다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://threejs.org/\">Three.js</a></p>\n<br>\n<p>API 관련 사이트</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sketchfab.com/developers/viewer/initialization\">Viewer API</a></p>\n<br>\n<p>참고 글\n<a href=\"https://medevel.com/16-webgl-opensource-frameworks/\">20 Open Source WebGL Frameworks</a></p>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#webgl-%EC%9D%B4%EB%9E%80\">WebGL 이란?</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<br>\n<br>","excerpt":"WebGL 이란? WebGL은 OpenGL을 기반으로 하는 JavaScript API / Library로 웹 브라우저가 추가 플러그인, 타사 플로그인 또는 브라우저 확장 프로그램을 설치할 필요 없이 브라우저에서 3D / 2D 그래픽을 렌더링을 도와준다. WebGL을 사용하면 브라우저를 통해 GPU를 사용하여 3D 그래픽을 HTML 페이지로 렌더링 할 수 있다.  Three.js 아래 사이트는 다양한 개발 샘플이 있다. Three.js API 관련 사이트 Viewer API 참고 글\n20 Open Source WebGL Frameworks WebGL 이란?","frontmatter":{"date":"June 29, 2022","title":"여러가지 오픈 소스 WebGL FrameWork","categories":"WebGL","author":"Crong","emoji":"🏹"},"fields":{"slug":"/WebGL/introduce/"}},"next":{"id":"cada63ee-137d-5680-b108-dd66ccaa8365","html":"<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 52.222222222222214%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"./typescript-logo.png\"\n        title=\"./typescript-logo.png\"\n        src=\"/static/0666e73f8a07ac7d3a7179026c62dd82/37523/typescript-logo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0666e73f8a07ac7d3a7179026c62dd82/e9ff0/typescript-logo.png 180w,\n/static/0666e73f8a07ac7d3a7179026c62dd82/f21e7/typescript-logo.png 360w,\n/static/0666e73f8a07ac7d3a7179026c62dd82/37523/typescript-logo.png 720w,\n/static/0666e73f8a07ac7d3a7179026c62dd82/ea7fb/typescript-logo.png 788w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<br>\n<h1 id=\"destructuring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#destructuring\" aria-label=\"destructuring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Destructuring</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>비구조화 할당</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> Object <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Crong'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    age<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">22</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    genger<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'male'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>위의 객체에서 <code class=\"language-text\">name</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">age</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">gender</code>를 각각 분리해서 사용하고자 할 때 <code class=\"language-text\">destructuring</code>을 사용한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"javascript에서의-destructuring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#javascript%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-destructuring\" aria-label=\"javascript에서의 destructuring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JavaScript에서의 Destructuring</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gender <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"typescript에서의-destructuring\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#typescript%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-destructuring\" aria-label=\"typescript에서의 destructuring permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>TypeScript에서의 Destructuring</h2>\n<h3 id=\"잘못된-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%98%EB%AA%BB%EB%90%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"잘못된 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>잘못된 방법</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gender<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>단순히 생각해서 이런 식으로 타입을 지정해주면 되지 않을까 싶었음</li>\n<li>이렇게 할 경우 name, age, gender를 각각 string,number,string으로 명명하라는 코드가 됨.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"쉬운-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%89%AC%EC%9A%B4-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"쉬운 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>쉬운 방법</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gender<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> age<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gender<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">{}</code>로 감싸진 전체에 대해서 타입을 지정해야 됨</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"권장하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B6%8C%EC%9E%A5%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\" aria-label=\"권장하는 방법 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>권장하는 방법</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">interface</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Props</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    age<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    gender<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">string</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> age<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gender <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Props <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Object<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>interface로 미리 타입을 정의하고 해당 interface를 타입으로 지정하는 방식이 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"table-of-contents\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#javascript%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-destructuring\">JavaScript에서의 Destructuring</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#typescript%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EC%9D%98-destructuring\">TypeScript에서의 Destructuring</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%9E%98%EB%AA%BB%EB%90%9C-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">잘못된 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%89%AC%EC%9A%B4-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">쉬운 방법</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EA%B6%8C%EC%9E%A5%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94-%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%95\">권장하는 방법</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"date":"June 20, 2022","title":"TypeScript - 비구조화 할당(Destructuring)","categories":"TypeScript Javascript","author":"Crong","emoji":"🎐"},"fields":{"slug":"/typescript/destructuring/"}},"prev":null,"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"https://sinde530.github.io","comments":{"utterances":{"repo":""}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/WebGL/intro